    <briefdescription>
<para>Compile-time acknowledgement gate for RADLib public SDK consumers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Public RADLib headers require an explicit license acknowledgement macro for external builds. This is a legal/compliance checkpoint, not DRM. Commercial applications should also verify a signed node-locked license at runtime with <ref refid="classRADSecurity_1_1LicenseManager" kindref="compound">RADSecurity::LicenseManager</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
